@node distribution
@title "Distribution"

 The 'AMP-Legacy' skin for AmigaAMP is Copyright İ 1998 by Georg Rottlaender.

 'AMP-Legacy' may be freely distributed as long as the following conditions  are
 fulfilled:

 - all files have to be kept together and

 - no file may be modified (especially the skin - IFF files - itself).

 Including this transfer animation in a commercial or shareware distribution  is
 prohibited without my written  permission.

 ... also it's prohibited to use this skin on a vapour-chip ...

@endnode

